"{\"uid\": \"canberratimes.com.au-story-8704411-australian-tourist-reports-rape-in-paris-ahead-of-the-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited news content and The Canberra Times app.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Canberra Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Canberra_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Premium subscribers also enjoy interactive puzzles and access to the digital version of our print edition - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The national Olympic team has been briefed on safety risks after an Australian tourist was allegedly raped by a group of men in Paris.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 342, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9988655483780896, \"rank\": 0.0010130041508869955, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1329393621409751e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  The 25-year-old woman sought refuge in a kebab shop on Boulevard de Clichy in Paris' 18tharrondissement, near The Moulin Rouge at 5am on July 20, according to French police.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulevard_de_Clichy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boulevard de Clichy\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulevard_de_Clichy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boulevard_de_Clichy\"}, {\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1329393621409751e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.458198840421604e-23, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}, {\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.051479502867599e-35, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Members of the Australian Olympic team have been urged to leave their national uniforms at the Athletes' Village and travel in groups after news of the attack emerged.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9967481842969922, \"rank\": 0.0032624245064199, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The alleged victim was found \\\"stunned\\\" with her dress partly torn off and backwards,French newspaper Le Parisienreported.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian tourist, who reportedly could not speak French, told police that she had been raped by five men earlier that night but was unable to provide further details.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.924192563159458e-38, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was taken to Bichat-Claude Bernard Hospital.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Australian Embassy in Paris is making urgent enquiries with French authorities following reports of an Australian citizen assaulted in Paris,\\\" a Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade spokesperson said.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1329393621409751e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9918093933408451, \"rank\": 0.008172748613767166, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9988655483780896, \"rank\": 0.0010130041508869955, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1329393621409751e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade stands ready to provide consular assistance.\\\"\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris' Prosecutor's Office said \\\"the investigation into the charge of gang rape likely to have been committed on the night of July 19 to 20 has been entrusted to the 2nd judicial police district\\\".\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1329393621409751e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Investigators would \\\"do everything to quickly identify the individuals and bring them to justice\\\", the prosecutor's office said.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This comes astourists flood to the European capital for the 2024 Paris Olympic Gamesfrom July 26 to August 11.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian chef de mission Anna Meares said she was \\\"waiting on further information on the actual case itself\\\" but told media that the Olympic team had been briefed on safety risks on July 23.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1879, \"end\": 1889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.9988655483780896, \"rank\": 0.0010130041508869955, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 1906, \"end\": 1917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What information we are passing onto our athletes is that security presence is really, really high and that's in order for them to act as quickly as possible to keep them safe,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not yet have any feedback from our athletes that they have felt unsafe - we are encouraging them, if they go out of the village, not to go out on their own, not to wear (their) team uniform, just to wear plain clothes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Support is available for those who may be distressed:  Anna Houlahan reports on crime and social issues affecting regional and remote Australia in her role as national crime reporter at Australian Community Media (ACM).\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\", \"score\": 0.9553789821202968, \"rank\": 0.04670452638896456, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\"}, {\"begin\": 2625, \"end\": 2634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9994519392919844, \"rank\": 0.0005483606521464032, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was ACM's Trainee of the Year in 2023 and, aside from reporting on crime, has travelled the country as a journalist for Explore Travel Magazine.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_for_Computing_Machinery\", \"score\": 0.999998283970507, \"rank\": 1.7086850400030434e-06, \"text\": \"ACM\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_for_Computing_Machinery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_for_Computing_Machinery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach out with news or updates to anna.houlahan@austcommunitymedia.com.au  Anna Houlahan reports on crime and social issues affecting regional and remote Australia in her role as national crime reporter at Australian Community Media (ACM).\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2935, \"end\": 2939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\", \"score\": 0.9553789821202968, \"rank\": 0.04670452638896456, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Windass\"}, {\"begin\": 3014, \"end\": 3023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9994519392919844, \"rank\": 0.0005483606521464032, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was ACM's Trainee of the Year in 2023 and, aside from reporting on crime, has travelled the country as a journalist for Explore Travel Magazine.\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3108, \"end\": 3111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_for_Computing_Machinery\", \"score\": 0.999998283970507, \"rank\": 1.7086850400030434e-06, \"text\": \"ACM\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Association_for_Computing_Machinery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http: